{"name": "Warm in the Winter", "ingredients": [{"quantity": "2 1/4", "item": "Citadelle gin", "unit": "oz", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "2 1/4", "item": "Krogstad Festlig aquavit", "unit": "oz", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "3/4", "item": "Laura's mix*", "unit": "oz", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "2 1/4", "item": "Fresh lime juice", "unit": "oz", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "1 1/2", "item": "Guava juice", "unit": "oz", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "1 1/2", "item": "Pineapple juice", "unit": "oz", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "3/4", "item": "Sugar cane syrup", "unit": "oz", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "12", "item": "Pepper tincture", "unit": "dashes", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "12", "item": "Bittermens Elemakule Tiki bitters", "unit": "dashes", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "6", "item": "Orchids, for garnish", "unit": "", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "6", "item": "Pineapple fronds, for garnish", "unit": "", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "3", "item": "Cheetah (or plain) straws, for garnish", "unit": "", "isGarnish": false}, {"quantity": "1", "item": "Flaming lime shell, for garnish**", "unit": "", "isGarnish": false}], "preparation": "This completely vegan cocktail takes Tiki to a dramatic level.\n\nWhip the gin, aquavit, Laura\u2019s mix, juices, syrup, tincture and bitters, pour into a metal nautilus shell (or similarly shaped vessel), top with crushed ice, and garnish with 6 orchids, 6 pineapple fronds, 3 cheetah-print (or plain) straws and a flaming lime shell.\n\n*Laura's mix: Combine 1 oz of banana liqueur, 1 oz of dry cura\u00e7ao and 2 oz of cinnamon syrup.\n\n**Flaming lime shell: Scoop out half a lime (or use what\u2019s left after juicing), then add a splash of overproof rum and light the flame when serving.", "imageURL": "https://www.liquor.com/thmb/De8uc3-zLAMOGZ9LSeqD-uVL2tk=/960x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__liquor__201